    <div id='header'></div>

    <h1 class='page-title'>Christmas Dumberland</h1>

    <h3>Hey {{to_name}}!</h3>

    <p class='intro-text'>
    Will it scratch? Will it bite?<br>
    Will it be a bloodcurdling sight?<br>
    {{from_name}} sent you a Dumb Present, whatâ€™s inside?
    </p>

    <div class='santa-present-dance' data-json='santa_present_dance.json'>
      <div></div>
    </div>

    <div class='row buttons-cont'>
      <div class='col-md-4'>&nbsp;</div>
      <div class='col-md-4'>
